[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_0",
    "text": "高考抢分晨读材料之六",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.31275720164609055,
      0.04130308318789994,
      0.7101704879482658,
      0.07329842931937172
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_1",
    "text": "身（代指蒙恬本人）虽（即使）囚系（表被动，即“被拘囚、遭到拘囚”）其（此处表示第一人称）势（即 “势力”）足以倍畔（通假字，即“背叛”）然……者（译为“但是……的原因”）不敢辱先人之教（即 “不敢辱没先人的教导”）以不忘先主也（以表示不忘先主的恩德）",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13011953752694494,
      0.09365910413030831,
      0.8935920047031158,
      0.14659685863874344
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_2",
    "text": "【整句翻译】",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13168724279835392,
      0.14834205933682373,
      0.8943758573388203,
      0.18440954043048283
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_3",
    "text": "文化常识",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.13247109543405838,
      0.1948807446189645,
      0.23907505388986872,
      0.21873182082606166
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_4",
    "text": "1.服阕：是指旧时官员 守丧期满除服。官员遭逢父母去世，按例要 守丧， 满三年后朝廷再授予 的职务。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12855183225553596,
      0.2257126236183828,
      0.8888888888888888,
      0.2606166375799884
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_5",
    "text": "2.农历：是我国长期采用的一种传统历法，它以 的周期来定月，因这种历法安排了 以指导农业生产活动，故称农历，又叫中历、夏历，俗称 O",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13247109543405838,
      0.2629435718440954,
      0.8943758573388203,
      0.2972658522396742
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_6",
    "text": "3.刺史制度：是中国古代重要的地方 制度。始于 ，完善于汉，东汉以后刺史成 为州郡最高 长官，有时称为太守。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13011953752694494,
      0.2990110529377545,
      0.8920242994317068,
      0.3333333333333333
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_7",
    "text": "4.殿试：是科举制 的考试。录取分三甲：一甲三名，统称“进士及第”，其中第一名称 9 第二名称 ，第三名称 。二、三甲的第一名皆称为 。一、二、三甲统称进士。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12855183225553596,
      0.3356602675974404,
      0.8951597099745248,
      0.3717277486910995
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_8",
    "text": "作文审题",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.13325494806976287,
      0.38219895287958117,
      0.23907505388986872,
      0.40430482838859805
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_9",
    "text": "2020 年9 月8日，被授予“人民英雄”国家荣誉称号的陈薇走上领奖台，眼尖的母亲一眼发现 了女儿的变化：“变老了，她以前头发没有一根白的，这次白了，她真的太操心了。”2020年9月9日， 回忆获颁共和国勋章的时刻，84 岁的钟南山说：“我故意在走红毯领奖时走快一点，显示我还没老。”",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12933568489124045,
      0.4089586969168121,
      0.8959435626102292,
      0.46131471785922046
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_10",
    "text": "进高三，有的同学懒散，有的同学迷茫，有的同学焦虑。请结合以上材料内涵，写一篇发稿， 在即将到来的200天誓师大会上发，帮助同学提振精神，更好地投学习。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1262002743484225,
      0.46364165212332753,
      0.8928081520674114,
      0.4985456660849331
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_11",
    "text": "要求：结合材料，选好度，确定意，明确体，拟标题；不要套作，不得抄袭；不得泄 露个人信息；不少于 800 字。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12933568489124045,
      0.5002908667830134,
      0.8935920047031158,
      0.535194880744619
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_12",
    "text": "审题立意",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.46952772878698806,
      0.5485747527632344,
      0.5510484029002547,
      0.5648632926119838
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_13",
    "text": "【审题】",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.18185381148344112,
      0.578824898196626,
      0.24377816970409563,
      0.5939499709133217
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_14",
    "text": "同学的身份。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5220458553791887,
      0.578824898196626,
      0.6200274348422496,
      0.5945317044793484
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_16",
    "text": "1.这是一道关于人物材料的任务驱动型作 文题目。材料叙述的是两位英雄人物陈薇和钟 南山领取奖章背后的故事。陈薇为国由青春到 白发，钟南山为国即使年老仍充满激情。因此， 我们主要围绕青春、激情、奉献、担当来立意。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14266117969821673,
      0.5968586387434555,
      0.501665686850872,
      0.6858638743455497
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_15",
    "text": "【参考立意】",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.5620223398001176,
      0.5974403723094822,
      0.656084656084656,
      0.612565445026178
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_17",
    "text": "1.历经岁月，青春不老。 2.心有激情，青春常在。 3.不负青春，为国担当。 4.心有家国，激情满怀。 5.青春耀前路，奋斗永不老。 6.青春激扬家国梦，心旌撼动未来情。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5541838134430727,
      0.6148923792902851,
      0.8418577307466196,
      0.7230948225712623
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_18",
    "text": "2.题干要求写一篇发言稿，就要运用发言 稿的格式，注意发言的情境，明确自己与在场",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14344503233392122,
      0.68760907504363,
      0.501665686850872,
      0.7230948225712623
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_19",
    "text": "诗歌鉴赏",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.13325494806976287,
      0.7527632344386271,
      0.23907505388986872,
      0.774869109947644
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_20",
    "text": "水调歌头·多景楼",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.440525181265922,
      0.7899941826643397,
      0.5824025083284342,
      0.806282722513089
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_21",
    "text": "[宋] 陆游",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.4703115814226925,
      0.8086096567771961,
      0.5573192239858906,
      0.8225712623618383
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_22",
    "text": "江左占形胜，最数古徐州。连山如画，佳处缥缈著危楼。鼓角临风悲壮，烽火连空明灭，往事忆孙刘。 千里曜戈甲，万灶宿貔貅。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13247109543405838,
      0.8272251308900523,
      0.8912404467960023,
      0.8603839441535777
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_23",
    "text": "露沾草，风落木，岁方秋。使君宏放，谈笑洗尽古今愁。不见襄阳登览，磨灭游人无数，遗恨黯难收。 叔子独千载，名与汉江流。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13325494806976287,
      0.8632926119837114,
      0.8928081520674114,
      0.8970331588132635
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 24
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544_24",
    "text": "赏析 词的上追忆历史物，下写今登临所怀，全词发出了对古今的感慨之情，表现了作",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.157554379776602,
      0.8993600930773705,
      0.8959435626102292,
      0.9168121000581734
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1544",
    "order": 25
  }
]